{"timestamp": "2025-12-03 20:57:09.821790", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission accepted.\n\nSummary of submission:\n- is_anomaly: true\n- faulty_devices: [\"switch_1\"]\n- root_cause_name: [\"p4_table_entry_misconfig\"]\n\nDiagnosis notes (concise):\n- switch_1 is installing/using incorrect ethernet.dst (MAC) values (e.g., 66660a666602) in the ipv4_forward action for ipv4_lpm entries, causing L2 mismatch and packet drops at hosts.\n- Likely cause is control-plane / table-entry formatting or encoding bug when populating switch_1's P4 table entries.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 2388, "output_tokens": 122, "total_tokens": 2510, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 1664}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
